<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Clubhouse - Join the Club</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Become an admin!</h1>
    <p><strong>It's simple:</strong> You just need to enter the secret passcode, and you will become an admin!</p>

    <form action="/become-admin" method="POST">
        <label for="passcode">Passcode:</label>
        <input id="passcode" name="passcode" required>
        <button type="submit">Confirm</button>
    </form>

    <% if(error) { %>
        <p style="color: red;"><%= error %></p>
        <p><strong>Hint:</strong> The correct passcode is NOT the one you just entered!</p>
   <% } %>
</body>
</html>